The [[upper case]] [[symbol]] for [[beta]] (''βήτα''), the second [[letter]] of the modern [[w:Greek alphabet|Greek alphabet]]. It is preceded by '''Α''', '''α''' and followed by '''Γ''', '''γ'''. The [[lower case]] symbol is '''β'''. 

